data.description: Welcome to Kingsbury Square! This home is on a peaceful cul de sac. Check out the large front porch and step inside to the gleaming hardwood floors throughout the main level. The living room is the heart of this home with a cozy gas fireplace providing warmth and ambiance. Next, you'll experience formal dining with a bay window and tons of natural light. The deck, kitchen, and bathrooms were beautifully updated in 2018. The Kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, there's a large primary suite, complete with a bay window and custom closet. Two more bedrooms feature custom closets and ceiling fans.The basement offers a bonus rm perfect for an office. 2-car tandem garage offers plenty of room for parking. New windows, new flooring in 2019. Brand new AC in 2023. Neighborhood is walking distance to Forest Park, Wash U/BJC, and Delmar Loop. Property is eligible for the The Live Near Your Work program for WashU/BJC employees.
